&lt;h3 id="quadruped-platform">Quadruped Platform&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>Four-legged robot platform for reinforcement learning locomotion experiments and sim-to-real transfer research, built alongside the bipedal work as part of the same hardware studio.&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;h3 id="community--mission">Community &amp;amp; Mission&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>All projects are fully open-source and documented — reproducible by anyone with access to a 3D printer and basic electronics. The goal is to &lt;strong>democratize embodied AI hardware&lt;/strong> and accelerate the research-to-product cycle for students and researchers across China.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>OpenDuckMini — 开源双足机器人</title><link>https://miracle-techlink.github.io/vivid-aurora-space/zh/projects/openduck-mini/</link><pubDate>Sat, 01 Nov 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://miracle-techlink.github.io/vivid-aurora-space/zh/projects/openduck-mini/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;strong>OpenDuckMini&lt;/strong> 是与
联合开发的开源微型双足机器人平台，子豪兄是国内最具影响力的 AI 科普创作者之一。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>硬件配置：&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>3D 打印结构件（PLA/PETG）&lt;/li>
&lt;li>各关节舵机驱动&lt;/li>
&lt;li>树莓派板载计算&lt;/li>
&lt;li>自制 PCB 线束&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>运动能力：&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>动态双足行走与奔跑步态&lt;/li>
&lt;li>已在大学跑道实地测试&lt;/li>
&lt;li>开源硬件设计，社区可完整复现&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>社区生态：&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>完整组装文档发布于飞书 Wiki&lt;/li>
&lt;li>隶属与子豪兄在同济大学联合创立的机器人工作室&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>本项目体现了一个核心理念：&lt;strong>具身 AI 硬件民主化&lt;/strong> — 让任何人都能构建并实验足式机器人，加速从研究到产品的转化周期。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>演示视频详见
或项目文档。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>LeRobot &amp; Embodied AI Hackathon Projects</title><link>https://miracle-techlink.github.io/vivid-aurora-space/projects/lerobot-embodied/</link><pubDate>Wed, 01 Oct 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://miracle-techlink.github.io/vivid-aurora-space/projects/lerobot-embodied/</guid><description>
