&lt;p>&lt;strong>Connection to research:&lt;/strong>
LeRobot&amp;rsquo;s flow-matching policy backbone directly informed the GDN-Memory integration work — understanding the inference pipeline was prerequisite to designing sub-1ms memory update scheduling.&lt;/p>
